%%{init: {'flowchart': {'curve': 'stepAfter', 'nodeSpacing': 30, 'rankSpacing': 40}}}%%
flowchart LR
    classDef startEnd fill:#000,stroke:#000,color:#fff
    classDef decision fill:#FFD700,stroke:#B8860B,color:#000
    classDef activity fill:#fff,stroke:#000,color:#000

    Start((Start)):::startEnd

    Start --> UserValid[User<br/>Validation]:::activity
    UserValid --> AuthCheck{Login<br/>Failed}:::decision
    AuthCheck -->|Yes| ForgotPW[Forgot Password]:::activity
    ForgotPW --> ResetPW[Reset<br/>Password]:::activity
    ResetPW --> UserValid
    AuthCheck -->|No| Dashboard[Display Free<br/>SOC Dashboard]:::activity
    Dashboard --> D1{Action?}:::decision

    D1 -->|Logout| Logout[Log out]:::activity
    Logout --> EndL((End)):::startEnd

    D1 -->|View Alerts| AlertList[View Alert<br/>List]:::activity
    AlertList --> AlertSub{Alert<br/>action?}:::decision
    AlertSub -->|View Detail| AlertDetail[View Alert<br/>Detail]:::activity
    AlertDetail --> MA{More<br/>Actions<br/>to do}:::decision
    AlertSub -->|Filter| FilterAlerts[Filter Alerts by<br/>Severity / Protocol]:::activity
    FilterAlerts --> MA
    AlertSub -->|Search| SearchAlerts[Search Alerts<br/>by IP / Keyword]:::activity
    SearchAlerts --> MA
    AlertSub -->|Block IP| BlockIP[Block / Unblock<br/>IP Address]:::activity
    BlockIP --> MA

    D1 -->|GeoIP Map| GeoIP[View GeoIP<br/>Threat Map]:::activity
    GeoIP --> MB{More<br/>Actions<br/>to do}:::decision

    D1 -->|Threat Intel| Threats[View Threat<br/>Intelligence]:::activity
    Threats --> Correlate[View IP Threat<br/>Correlation]:::activity
    Correlate --> MB

    D1 -->|Real-Time Alerts| WSAlerts[Receive WebSocket<br/>Alert Notifications]:::activity
    WSAlerts --> MB

    D1 -->|Demo Simulation| Demo[Run Demo<br/>Simulation]:::activity
    Demo --> DemoResults[View Demo<br/>Summary Results]:::activity
    DemoResults --> MC{More<br/>Actions<br/>to do}:::decision

    D1 -->|DurianBot| Chat[Use DurianBot<br/>Basic Chat]:::activity
    Chat --> MC

    D1 -->|View Subscription| ViewSub[View Subscription<br/>Details]:::activity
    ViewSub --> UpgradeQ{Upgrade<br/>plan?}:::decision
    UpgradeQ -->|Yes| Upgrade[Upgrade via<br/>Stripe Payment]:::activity
    Upgrade --> MD{More<br/>Actions<br/>to do}:::decision
    UpgradeQ -->|No| MD

    D1 -->|Manage Whitelist| Whitelist[Add / Remove<br/>Whitelisted IPs]:::activity
    Whitelist --> MD

    D1 -->|Manage Blocked IPs| BlockedIPs[View / Unblock<br/>Blocked IPs]:::activity
    BlockedIPs --> MD

    MA -->|Yes| Dashboard
    MB -->|Yes| Dashboard
    MC -->|Yes| Dashboard
    MD -->|Yes| Dashboard

    MA -->|No| E1((End)):::startEnd
    MB -->|No| E2((End)):::startEnd
    MC -->|No| E3((End)):::startEnd
    MD -->|No| E4((End)):::startEnd
